{"tid":1361391,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[727] 千萬不要忘記元朗同天水圍警署","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T15:15:12.000Z","uid":9846,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"54a7dc5e22ea10ed9fbaf2db342f86c6d12c524a","tid":1361391,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8b69vjv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8b69vjv.png&h=2e1509de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n27號晚，香港警察已經正名成為政治工具，所謂保護秩序，保障市民生命財產等只係一個藉口，讓前線警員打得心安理得。<br />\n<br />\n小弟建議元朗反黑遊行，大家可以送個鐘比香港警察，一方面寓意香港嘅治安已經壽終正寢，另一方面想比元朗前線嘅警務人員睇清楚時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5JjGmuF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5JjGmuF.png&h=cc4d2ba7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65ea4d83a949260170ce86f282d35090c78563a6","tid":1361391,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"⌚️"},{"pid":"c4c95d2793d63bdc610009cfd9495ccded0f2488","tid":1361391,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:01:35.000Z","msg":"⏰"},{"pid":"79a55edd96f5619355f6da26e57cafa297efe11b","tid":1361391,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:01:46.000Z","msg":"🕰"},{"pid":"dd008efc9c69179b19a91d6cd6034c60bc7a18b7","tid":1361391,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"🕐"},{"pid":"0210f1de9ace63c54eb9e2cd74932c30bb089581","tid":1361391,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:02:06.000Z","msg":"🕑"},{"pid":"d15ba01ca01566db71e72d657a107ce4da63121a","tid":1361391,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:02:06.000Z","msg":"【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+攻破白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361315\" data-auto-link 